===Etymology===
From ''[[neep]]'' + an unknown first element.  Compare ''[[parsnip]]''.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈtɜ:nɪp/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The white root of a yellow-flowered plant, ''Brassica rapa'', grown as a vegetable and as food for cattle.
# (''Scotland'') The [[swede]].

